                  day-5 Database Assignment Questions

1)write a query to fetch employee names whose name ends with 's'
 and has five character
2)count the employee in each deptartment
3)dept wise show the minimum salary
4)show only those dept name whose max salary is > 60000
5)find the second highest salary from employee
6)show the all employee names except tester

all are basic only i have given

solution:---
1) select * from employee where name like '%s';
2) select dept,count(id) from employee group by dept;
3) select dept,count(id), min(salary) from employee group by dept;

4) select dept  from employee where salary>60000;
2) select max(salary) from employee where salary not in (select max(salary) from employee);
6) select name from employee where dept='tester';

